name: The Golden-Alien-Beetle
description:
This generative artwork was made using vqgan-clip + pencil hand drawn of a beetle.
My inspiration for the source image was seeing a dog eat a beetle. I had to make that moment last forever.
The sounds of it I'll never forget. You can imagine it. I'm sorry.
The golden shiny aspect comes from ancient Egypt jewelry.

Res. 1920 x 1920
